# Generated artifacts — collapsed in GitHub diffs and excluded from language
# stats. They are still tracked and required on disk; this only stops them from
# adding review noise. Reviewers can always expand them manually.

# Drizzle migration metadata: snapshots are the state drizzle-kit diffs against
# to generate the next migration, and _journal.json is its ordering ledger.
# Both are machine-generated by `pnpm db:generate`. The *.sql migration files
# are intentionally NOT marked generated — that DDL runs against production and
# must be reviewed.
#
# Matched directory-agnostically so any package's drizzle meta is covered
# (libs/database/drizzle/meta, libs/agent-daemon-state/drizzle-pg/meta,
# libs/agent-daemon-state/drizzle-sqlite/meta, and any future ones).
**/meta/*_snapshot.json linguist-generated=true
**/meta/_journal.json linguist-generated=true
